    <content>&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Hi everyone,&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;We upgraded from Build Apps free plan to Build Apps standard plan following this:&amp;nbsp;&lt;A href="https://help.sap.com/docs/build-apps/service-guide/upgrade-to-sap-build-apps-standard-edition?q=import" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;https://help.sap.com/docs/build-apps/service-guide/upgrade-to-sap-build-apps-standard-edition?q=import&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;We had 56 projects in the free plan, that we exported as recommended in order to import them back to Build Apps standard plan once installed.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;However, instead of having 0 project in the brand new standard plan like in the tutorial video, we noticed that 19 projects were already listed there. We tried to import a project that was not in the list but we keep having the following error message:&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;IMPORT FAILED&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Project eu10.yjdhdjdj… already exists&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Correlation Id: 748h67….&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;span class="lia-inline-image-display-wrapper lia-image-align-inline" image-alt="2025-04-24 15_55_49-SAP BuildBug.png" style="width: 877px;"&gt;&lt;img src="https://community.sap.com/t5/image/serverpage/image-id/254429iB8B43238F7261FFF/image-size/large?v=v2&amp;amp;px=999" role="button" title="2025-04-24 15_55_49-SAP BuildBug.png" alt="2025-04-24 15_55_49-SAP BuildBug.png" /&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;We saw the following note but unless mistaken it seems to suggest no solution:&amp;nbsp;&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;A href="https://me.sap.com/notes/0003521702" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;https://me.sap.com/notes/0003521702&lt;/A&gt;&lt;/P&gt;&lt;P&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Just contacted SAP Support about it but if anyone of you knows how to fix this, that would be really appreciated.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;Thanks,&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;BR,&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;BR /&gt;&lt;SPAN&gt;LM.&lt;/SPAN&gt;&lt;/P&gt;</content>
